sql_statement.static: SELECT testphase AS test, TxOk, NULL AS RateOk, NULL AS FlrOk, NULL AS FtdOk, NULL AS FdvOk, curr AS ServiceId,
CASE WHEN testphase='CIR' THEN step ELSE 'NA' END AS Step, Color, NULL AS StepLoad,

COALESCE(CASE WHEN SUM(rx.L1BitCount) * L2Factor > 0.0005 * SUM(rx.LastArrivalTime - rx.FirstArrivalTime) THEN ROUND((SUM(rx.L1BitCount) * L2Factor / SUM(rx.LastArrivalTime - rx.FirstArrivalTime))-0.0005, 3) END, 0) AS IrMean,
COALESCE(SUM(TxFrameCount - rx.FrameCount), SUM(TxFrameCount)) AS FlCount,
(1e2 * COALESCE(SUM(TxFrameCount - rx.FrameCount)/ SUM(TxFrameCount), 1)) AS Flr,
SUM(TxFrameCount) AS TxFrameCount, COALESCE(SUM(rx.FrameCount), 0) AS RxFrameCount,
SUM(rx.TotalLatency) AS FtdTotal,
COALESCE(MIN(rx.MinLatency) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FtdMin,
COALESCE(SUM(rx.TotalLatency)/SUM(rx.FrameCount) * 1e-5, 'NA') AS FtdMean,
COALESCE(MAX(rx.Maxlatency) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FtdMax,
SUM(rx.TotalJitter) AS FdvTotal,
COALESCE(MIN(rx.MinJitter) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FdvMin,
COALESCE(SUM(rx.TotalJitter)/SUM(rx.FrameCount) * 1e-5, 'NA') AS FdvMean,
COALESCE(MAX(rx.MaxJitter) * 1e-3, 'NA') AS FdvMax
FROM (SELECT Sb.Active AS SbActive, Sb.L2Rate/Sb.BpsLoad AS L2Factor, Sb.Handle AS SbHandle,
COALESCE(Tx.FrameCount>=0,0) AS TxOk, COALESCE(Tx.FrameCount, 0) AS TxFrameCount,
UPPER(SUBSTR(Tag.Name,1,1)) || SUBSTR(Tag.Name,2,LENGTH(Tag.Name)-15) AS Color,
Tx.StreamId, Sb.ParentHnd
FROM StreamBlock AS Sb LEFT JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS Tx ON Sb.Handle=Tx.ParentStreamBlock
JOIN RelationTable AS rt ON Sb.Handle=rt.SourceHnd JOIN Tag ON Rt.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle) AS SbTx
LEFT JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS Rx ON StreamId=Comp32 AND (Rx.SigFrameCount IS NULL OR IsExpectedPort), y1564Iter
WHERE SbActive AND (test != 'CBS' OR Color !='Yellow') GROUP BY Color
SELECT * FROM (SELECT Test,
1 AS TxOk, null AS RateOk,
null AS FlrOk, null AS FtdOk, null AS FdvOk,
ServiceId, CASE WHEN testphase='CIR' THEN res.step ELSE 'NA' END AS Step,
'Total' AS Color,
SUM(StepLoad) AS StepLoad,
CASE WHEN SUM(IrMean)!=0 THEN ROUND(SUM(IrMean)-0.0005,3) ELSE 0 END AS IrMean, SUM(FlCount) AS FlCount,
1e2 * SUM(TxFrameCount - RxFrameCount) / SUM(TxFrameCount) AS Flr,
SUM(TxFrameCount) AS TxFrameCount,
SUM(RxFrameCount) AS RxFrameCount,
SUM(FtdTotal) AS FtdTotal,
CASE WHEN MAX(FtdMin)!='NA' THEN MIN(FtdMin) ELSE 'NA' END AS FtdMin,
COALESCE(SUM(FtdTotal)/SUM(RxFrameCount) * 1e-5, 'NA') AS FtdMean,
CASE WHEN MAX(FtdMin)!='NA' THEN MAX(FtdMax) ELSE 'NA' END AS FtdMax,
SUM(FdvTotal) AS FdvTotal,
CASE WHEN MAX(FdvMin)!='NA' THEN MIN(FdvMin) ELSE 'NA' END AS FdvMin,
COALESCE(SUM(FdvTotal)/SUM(RxFrameCount) * 1e-5, 'NA') AS FdvMean,
CASE WHEN MAX(FdvMax)!='NA' THEN MAX(FdvMax) ELSE 'NA' END AS FdvMax
FROM y1564Results AS res JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON curr=res.ServiceId WHERE Test=testphase)
WHERE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM y1564Results AS res JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON curr=res.ServiceId WHERE Test=testphase AND res.Color='Yellow')>0

Update y1564Results SET StepLoad=(SELECT (y1564Config.CIR/CirSteps*Step) FROM y1564Config, y1564Global WHERE ServiceId=y1564Config.rowid) WHERE Test=(SELECT testphase FROM y1564Iter) AND Step=(SELECT step FROM y1564Iter)
UPDATE y1564Results SET FlrOk=
(SELECT rt.Flr<=cf.FLR FROM y1564Results AS rt JOIN y1564Config AS cf ON cf.rowid=rt.ServiceId JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON cf.rowid=curr AND rt.Test=testphase WHERE rt.Color='Green')
WHERE Test=(SELECT testphase FROM y1564Iter) AND ServiceId=(SELECT curr FROM y1564Iter) AND (Step=(SELECT step FROM y1564Iter) OR (SELECT testphase!='CIR' FROM y1564Iter)) AND Color='Green'
UPDATE y1564Results SET FtdOk=

(SELECT rt.FtdMax IS NOT NULL AND rt.FtdMax<=cf.FTD FROM y1564Results AS rt JOIN y1564Config AS cf ON cf.rowid=rt.ServiceId JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON cf.rowid=curr AND rt.Test=testphase WHERE rt.Color='Green')
WHERE Test=(SELECT testphase FROM y1564Iter) AND ServiceId=(SELECT curr FROM y1564Iter) AND (Step=(SELECT step FROM y1564Iter) OR (SELECT testphase!='CIR' FROM y1564Iter)) AND Color='Green'
UPDATE y1564Results SET FdvOk=

(SELECT rt.FdvMax IS NOT NULL AND rt.FdvMax<=cf.FDV FROM y1564Results AS rt JOIN y1564Config AS cf ON cf.rowid=rt.ServiceId JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON cf.rowid=curr AND rt.Test=testphase WHERE rt.Color='Green')
WHERE Test=(SELECT testphase FROM y1564Iter) AND ServiceId=(SELECT curr FROM y1564Iter) AND (Step=(SELECT step FROM y1564Iter) OR (SELECT testphase!='CIR' FROM y1564Iter)) AND Color='Green'
UPDATE y1564Results SET RateOk=

(SELECT ROUND(rt.StepLoad*(1-cf.FLR/100.0)-0.0005,3)<=rt.IrMean FROM y1564Results AS rt JOIN y1564Config AS cf ON cf.rowid=rt.ServiceId JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON cf.rowid=curr AND rt.Test=testphase WHERE rt.Color='Green')
WHERE Test=(SELECT testphase FROM y1564Iter) AND ServiceId=(SELECT curr FROM y1564Iter) AND (Step=(SELECT step FROM y1564Iter) OR (SELECT testphase!='CIR' FROM y1564Iter)) AND Color='Green'
UPDATE y1564Results SET RateOk=

(SELECT rt.IrMean BETWEEN ROUND(CIR*(1-cf.FLR/100.0)-0.0005,3) AND CIR+EIR FROM y1564Results AS rt JOIN y1564Config AS cf ON cf.rowid=rt.ServiceId JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON cf.rowid=curr AND rt.Test=testphase WHERE rt.Color='Green')
WHERE Test=(SELECT testphase FROM y1564Iter) AND ServiceId=(SELECT curr FROM y1564Iter) AND (Step=(SELECT step FROM y1564Iter) OR (SELECT testphase!='CIR' FROM y1564Iter)) AND Color='Green'
UPDATE y1564Results SET RateOk=

(SELECT rt.IrMean BETWEEN ROUND(CIR*(1-cf.FLR/100.0)-0.0005,3) AND (1.01 * (CASE WHEN EIR<CIR*0.2 THEN CIR*1.25+EIR ELSE CIR+EIR*1.25 END)) FROM y1564Results AS rt JOIN y1564Config AS cf ON cf.rowid=rt.ServiceId JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON cf.rowid=curr AND rt.Test=testphase WHERE rt.Color='Green')
WHERE Test=(SELECT testphase FROM y1564Iter) AND ServiceId=(SELECT curr FROM y1564Iter) AND (Step=(SELECT step FROM y1564Iter) OR (SELECT testphase!='CIR' FROM y1564Iter)) AND Color='Green'
UPDATE y1564Results SET RateOk=

(SELECT rt.IrMean <= (1.01 * (CASE WHEN EIR<CIR*0.2 THEN CIR*1.25+EIR ELSE CIR+EIR*1.25 END)) FROM y1564Results AS rt JOIN y1564Config AS cf ON cf.rowid=rt.ServiceId JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON cf.rowid=curr AND rt.Test=testphase WHERE rt.Color='Total')
WHERE Test=(SELECT testphase FROM y1564Iter) AND ServiceId=(SELECT curr FROM y1564Iter) AND (Step=(SELECT step FROM y1564Iter) OR (SELECT testphase!='CIR' FROM y1564Iter)) AND Color='Green'
UPDATE y1564Results SET RateOk=

(SELECT rt.IrMean >= ROUND(CIR*(1-cf.FLR/100.0)-0.0005,3) FROM y1564Results AS rt JOIN y1564Config AS cf ON cf.rowid=rt.ServiceId JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON cf.rowid=curr AND rt.Test=testphase WHERE rt.Color='Green')
WHERE Test=(SELECT testphase FROM y1564Iter) AND ServiceId=(SELECT curr FROM y1564Iter) AND (Step=(SELECT step FROM y1564Iter) OR (SELECT testphase!='CIR' FROM y1564Iter)) AND Color='Green'

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS y1564Rates(Phase TEXT, FpsLoad FLOAT, AvgFrameSize INTEGER)

SELECT DISTINCT 'CIR' AS 'Phase',
FpsLoad AS 'FpsLoad',

JOIN RelationTable AS Rt ON SourceHnd=Sb.Handle
JOIN Tag ON Rt.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS y1564Rates(Phase TEXT, FpsLoad FLOAT, AvgFrameSize INTEGER)
DELETE FROM y1564Rates WHERE Phase!='CIR'
SELECT * FROM (
SELECT 'EIR' AS 'Phase', FpsLoad
, ROUND(L2Rate / FpsLoad / 8) AS 'AvgFrameSize'
FROM StreamBlock AS Sb JOIN RelationTable AS Rt ON SourceHnd=Sb.Handle
JOIN Tag ON Rt.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle WHERE Tag.Name='yellow_ttStreamBlock')
WHERE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM StreamBlock AS Sb JOIN RelationTable AS Rt ON SourceHnd=Sb.Handle
JOIN Tag ON Rt.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle WHERE Tag.Name='yellow_ttStreamBlock')>0
UNION SELECT * FROM (SELECT 'CIR+EIR' AS 'Phase', FpsLoad
, ROUND(L2Rate / FpsLoad / 8) AS 'AvgFrameSize'
FROM StreamBlock)
WHERE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM StreamBlock AS Sb JOIN RelationTable AS Rt On SourceHnd=Sb.Handle
JOIN Tag ON Rt.TargetHnd=Tag.Handle WHERE Tag.Name='yellow_ttStreamBlock')=0
INSERT INTO y1564Rates SELECT * FROM

(SELECT 'EIR' AS 'Phase', (SELECT FpsLoad FROM y1564Rates WHERE Phase='CIR+EIR') - (SELECT FpsLoad FROM y1564Rates WHERE Phase='CIR') AS 'FpsLoad', (SELECT AvgFrameSize FROM y1564Rates WHERE Phase='CIR') AS 'AvgFrameSize')
WHERE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM y1564Rates WHERE Phase='EIR')=0
UNION SELECT * FROM

(SELECT 'CIR+EIR' AS 'Phase', (SELECT FpsLoad FROM y1564Rates WHERE Phase='CIR') + (SELECT FpsLoad FROM y1564Rates WHERE Phase='EIR') AS 'FpsLoad', (SELECT AvgFrameSize FROM y1564Rates WHERE Phase='CIR') AS 'AvgFrameSize')
WHERE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM y1564Rates WHERE Phase='CIR+EIR')=0

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM y1564Results AS res JOIN y1564Iter ON res.ServiceId=curr WHERE NOT ((TxOK IS null OR TxOK) AND (RateOk IS null OR RateOk) AND (FlrOk IS null OR FlrOk) AND (FtdOk IS null OR FtdOk) AND (FdvOk IS null OR FdvOk)))>0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END

sql_statement.static: SELECT cf.ServiceName AS 'Service Name', Test AS 'Test',
CASE WHEN Test='CIR' THEN res.Step ELSE 'NA' END AS 'Step',
CASE WHEN (cf.ColorAware AND Test NOT IN ('CIR', 'CBS')) THEN res.Color ELSE 'NA' END AS 'Color',

CASE WHEN ((TxOk IS null OR TxOk) AND (RateOk IS null OR RateOk) AND (FlrOk IS null OR FlrOk) AND (FtdOk IS null OR FtdOk) AND (FdvOk IS null OR FdvOk)) THEN CASE WHEN COALESCE(RateOk,FlrOk,FtdOk,FdvOk) IS NOT NULL THEN 'PASS' ELSE 'NA' END ELSE 'FAIL' END AS 'PASS/FAIL',
CASE res.Test WHEN 'CIR' THEN CirDuration WHEN 'EIR' THEN EirDuration WHEN 'Policing' THEN PolicingDuration WHEN 'CBS' THEN CbsDuration WHEN 'EBS' THEN EbsDuration END AS 'Duration',
res.IrMean AS 'IR Mean (Mbit/s)', res.FlCount AS 'FL Count', ROUND(res.Flr, 3) AS 'FLR (%)',
ROUND(res.FtdMin, 5) AS 'FTD Min (ms)',
ROUND(res.FtdMean, 5) AS 'FTD Mean (ms)',
ROUND(res.FtdMax, 5) AS 'FTD Max (ms)',
ROUND(res.FdvMin, 5) AS 'FDV Min (ms)',
ROUND(res.FdvMean, 5) AS 'FDV Mean (ms)',
ROUND(res.FdvMax, 5) AS 'FDV Max (ms)'
FROM y1564Results AS res JOIN y1564Config AS cf ON res.ServiceId=cf.rowid JOIN y1564Iter AS it ON cf.rowid=curr, y1564Global ORDER BY res.ServiceId, res.rowid
